cd client

npm install

npm run dev


Install Tailwind CSS : 

npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer

npx tailwindcss init -p 

created file : tailwind.config.js , postcss.config.js

create folderes : context , components, pages

npm install react-router-dom

npm install react-toastify

npm install quill

npm run dev

npm install @clerk/clerk-react

npm i k-convert // convert ex: 10,000 to 10K

npm i moment // use for timestamp

npm i quill //

----------- Server ----------

create server folder
terminal -> npm init -y

npm i express

npm i jsonwebtoken //authentication for recruiter

npm i bcrypt // help in encrypt the user password

npm i mongoose nodemon svix // For connectiing with mongodb database and us enodemon for start server project

npm i cors multer dotenv cloudinary 
// cor for manage multiple origin 
// multer help for manage form data 
// dotenv manage environment variable 
// cloudinary manage store users resume and company logo in cloudinary platform

npm install @sentry/node --save //ExpressJs 

Use of : Sentry, Clerk, Vercel, MongoDB Atlas, Cloudinary, Svix, React-Toastify, K-Convert, Moment, Quill - For CRUD Login data

